index_getmaillist.title: Sep. 17th Scheduled Maintenance
index_getmaillist.content:
Dear Commanders,
We will be having our scheduled maintenance from September 17th 00:00 to 06:00 UTC-8.
Please be mindful that you will be unable to access the game during the maintenance period. 

1. Event: A special <color=#bf8f00>login event</color> will be held from <color=#bf8f00>Sep. 19th – Oct. 3rd</color> to celebrate the upcoming Neural Upgrade system. Login for 7 days in total to obtain various rewards including 3-star HG T-Doll <color=#bf8f00>P226</color>.

2. Added: <color=#bf8f00>Operation Cube+</color> will be added to Campaign as a permanent event after the maintenance! The related story playbacks will become accessible in the Index at the same time.
Limited drops: 4-star RF T-Doll <color=#bf8f00>Gr PSG-1</color>, 3-star SMG T-Doll <color=#bf8f00>Z-62</color>, 3-star AR T-Doll <color=#bf8f00>ARX-160</color>, 3-star AR T-Doll <color=#bf8f00>6P62</color>, 3-star T-Doll AR <color=#bf8f00>ASh-12.7</color> and 3-star MG T-Doll <color=#bf8f00>62 Shiki</color>.

3. Added: A <color=#bf8f00>public vote</color> for Neural Upgrade will be held from <color=#bf8f00>Sep. 17th – 19th</color>. Neural Upgrade is a feature that allows you to increase a T-Doll's level cap and grant them a second skill. This vote will decide which T-Dolls receive the Neural Upgrade first.

4. Added: 3-star SMG T-Doll <color=#bf8f00>Z-62</color>, 3-star AR T-Doll <color=#bf8f00>ARX-160</color> and 4-star RF T-Doll <color=#bf8f00>Gr PSG-1</color> will be added to the heavy production pool after the maintenance.

5. Fixed: The skill descriptions of Px4 Storm and K31.

6. Fixed: K31's specifications on the drop page.

Please note that any unfinished battles will be closed once the maintenance begins.
We would like to offer a Maintenance Reward to all players affected by the maintenance as an apology. Please be sure to check your mailbox and claim it.
Maintenance Reward: 500 Manpower, Ammo, Ration and Parts.

We sincerely apologize for the inconvenience.
Thank you for your understanding.

Girls' Frontline Operations Team
2019-09-16
